      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WEST ON HARRY (1) comes off an average performance last start when sixth at this track over 400m behind Bolt Of Fun (22.64) in a OPEN. Placed at his previous run. The form from his last run stacks up well. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. MAX CAPACITY (2) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (27.95) at this track behind RAPIDO KUNA in a Grade 4/5. Turned chasing the leaders but kept coming. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Can feature again. RAPIDO KUNA (4) goes very well at the course and distance with three wins and a placing from five starts. Scored by half a length last time (27.90) in a Grade 4/5 over 488m at this track. Looks one of the chances. ASTON WALKER (6) can run a bold race on best form.",
